author: Paul Cullen, Jack Horgan-Jones
title: Coronavirus: Varadkar says there will be delays in testing and results in coming weeks
description: Taoiseach says Ireland has decided ‘to do a lot of tests’
content:
Taoiseach Leo Varadkar has said there will be delays in Covid-19 tests and results in the coming weeks.
